data.description: This freshly updated brick ranch is perfect for anyone seeking a comfortable and convenient lifestyle in a great location. Living is easy in this single-story residence; perfect for first-time homebuyers, small families, or those looking to downsize.  Beautiful Carrara marble style tile throughout the living room and tastefully updated kitchen with navy blue cabinetry, brand-new stainless steel appliances, and huge pantry. Full bath updated nicely with barn door, modern subway tile, new faucet & floating vanity, and exhaust fan w built-in Bluetooth speaker. The spacious, private, and fully-fenced in backyard with large deck is ideal for entertaining or relaxing and features an oversized 2 car detached garage with plenty of area for storage. Newer roof (approx. 2017) and windows allowing plenty of natural light. New carpet in bedrooms and attic space with decking for additional storage! Conveniently situated in Westland, this property offers easy access to a variety of shopping centers, restaurants, parks, and Livonia school district schools. Two minute walk to Corrado Park. Commuting is a breeze with major highways and public transportation nearby, making it an excellent location for those working in neighboring cities.
